column2: SELECT TOP # emline.fiberid as fiberID, emline.ra, emline.dec,  emline.z as z_noqso, emline.zerr as z_noqso_err,  emline.sigmaStars as emline_vdisp, emline.sigmaStarsErr as emline_vdisp_err,  pca.vdisp_median as pca_vdisp, pca.vdisp_err as pca_vdisp_err,  sp.veldisp as sp_vdisp, sp.veldisperr as sp_vdisp_err  FROM emissionLinesPort AS emline  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# AS pca ON emline.specobjid = pca.specobjid  JOIN specObj as sp ON emline.specobjid = sp.specobjid  WHERE  pca.warning=# AND emline.z < # AND ABS(emline.sigmaStars-pca.vdisp_median)/emline.sigmaStars < #
